{"tid":1873854,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"手足，需要口罩嗎？","createTime":"2020-02-11T01:18:25.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-11T13:29:02.000Z","uid":247798,"like":20,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":19,"replies":[{"pid":"263f9b43601a3898f97167aa127a63e8f80b184d","tid":1873854,"uid":247798,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-11T01:18:25.000Z","msg":"入正題前，想提提大家今日係811半周年<br />\n<br />\n即係：<br />\n尖沙咀爆眼<br />\n葵芳站室內放TG<br />\n太古站一米內行刑式射胡椒球槍<br />\n銅鑼灣爆牙<br />\n被踢爆有狗扮手足<br />\n被捕手足送新屋嶺虐打性侵<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/kvCNtqJ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FkvCNtqJ.jpg&h=efaed8fd&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/v91Zjxo.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fv91Zjxo.jpg&h=56171344&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/9QeW6cp.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F9QeW6cp.jpg&h=c905ece9&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/sCHNtqK.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FsCHNtqK.jpg&h=1d2b000b&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/FFC5Zxq.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FFFC5Zxq.jpg&h=6ada22f5&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/GmUW6cq.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FGmUW6cq.jpg&h=adb16862&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/RfpwaD5.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FRfpwaD5.jpg&h=bee818b3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n入正題<br />\n<br />\n唔知仲有幾多手足上連登<br />\n不過都想盡自己小小既力幫下手<br />\n係唔同地方運物資（口罩，hand sanitizer等）返黎用成本價賣比手足或前線<br />\n<br />\n希望手足建議下篩選同交收方法<br />\n<br />\n另外亦想點下人頭有幾多人需要<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n最後<br />\n<br />\n光復香港 時代革命<br />\n五大訴求 缺一不可"},{"pid":"598abea48c32ac98afd65ffcd2388cb61ad38ba5","tid":1873854,"uid":247798,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-11T01:21:32.000Z","ms